      <div class="mb-14 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide mb-3" style="color:#4B5563;">FAQ</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-5" style="color:#1E2A3A;">Still have questions?</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        {[
          { q: "What fees do I pay to FlipSplit?", a: "Pure cash-offer sellers pay $0 in FlipSplit fees — you receive 100% of the amount we offer you. If you choose the profit-split path, we charge a 2.5% program fee for managing the renovation. Either way, standard seller closing costs (title, escrow, transfer taxes) apply and are itemized line-by-line before close — no hidden fees." },
          { q: "What if the renovated home doesn't sell for what you projected?", a: "Your upfront cash offer is yours regardless. FlipSplit carries 100% of the construction and downside market risk. The profit-split bonus only pays out if the renovated home sells above your offer — if the market underperforms, your upfront amount doesn't change. You're guaranteed the cash, not guaranteed the bonus." },
          { q: "Who decides what gets renovated, and will I see the budget?", a: "We do — but you receive our estimated renovation budget AND a projected resale price upfront, before you sign. No surprises. Once construction starts, our team manages every contractor, permit, and material." },
          { q: "Can I visit the property during construction?", a: "Unfortunately no — it's an insurance restriction during active work. Once renovations are complete, we'll happily schedule a walk-through preview before the home goes back on the market." },
          { q: "How fast can you buy my home?", a: "If you move quickly, we can close in as little as 48–72 hours. We can also accommodate timelines out to 90 days if you need more flexibility — the choice is yours." },
          { q: "Can I get cash before closing?", a: "Yes. We can advance you up to $20,000 prior to the close of escrow for cash-flow needs while you wait for the full payment at close." },
          { q: "When do I receive the profit-split bonus check?", a: "Within 10 days after the renovated home is resold. From your signing day to bonus-check delivery, expect roughly 90–120 days total depending on renovation scope and market conditions." },
          { q: "What kinds of homes do you buy?", a: "Any condition, any type — single-family homes, condos, distressed properties, inherited homes, tenant-occupied rentals, even homes already in great shape. We specialize in the situations other buyers won't touch, but we also work with sellers who just want a fast, hassle-free sale." },
          { q: "What areas does FlipSplit serve?", a: "We currently buy homes throughout Southern California — Los Angeles, Ventura, Orange, Riverside, San Bernardino, and San Diego counties. New markets are coming." },
          { q: "Can I leave trash or furniture behind when I sell?", a: "Yes. Take what you want, leave the rest. Trash, old furniture, even years of accumulated stuff — we've seen it all and handle the cleanout ourselves." },
        ].map(({ q, a }) => (
          <details class="group border-b border-slate-200 py-1">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-5 cursor-pointer font-semibold transition-colors hover:opacity-80" style="color:#1E2A3A;">
              {q}
